{"tid":1520904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[向香港警察宣言] 請立即重回正軌!","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T04:59:58.000Z","uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1885c2011e04814e9b8ed9842fe6efb4c206c83d","tid":1520904,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好再做賤賊啦<br />\n做返個警察<br />\n保障自己同埋身邊嘅香港人<br />\n蚑共又俾壓力你哋，香港人又俾壓力你哋!<br />\n蚑共壓力冇得走，但係香港人嘅壓力你哋可以避到!<br />\n咁你哋仲唔撚識揀? 盡力以功抵過! 改善返自己形象!<br />\n蚑那狗當你哋condom咋! 蚑那狗冇交稅俾你哋㗎!<br />\n係香港人交稅俾你哋呀!<br />\n你哋自己都交稅，但係好多都係養緊蚑那狗呀!<br />\n養狼狗，咬春袋呀! 你哋自己都養緊咬你春袋嘅狼狗呀!<br />\n蚑共機密文件已經話明要犧牲你哋，仲唔撚識做?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5RiW0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5RiW0i.jpg&h=adc4c549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚警察收工俾人斬，唔係香港人做嘅<br />\n絕對係蚑共啲order<br />\n唔好再將你哋「義憤」發洩落香港人身上<br />\n對準蚑共政權! 蚑共先係你哋嘅真正敵人!</span></span>"},{"pid":"a44c9dd69ed4ccfa58142d3884a33651d14942f1","tid":1520904,"uid":213379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"黑警Condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9232eb94e2f12b9edc54c7a561b14c93fc521a49","tid":1520904,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">功就白衫拎 屎就藍衫食</span></span>"},{"pid":"3e8d7ded93925fdbf1418c0696d77d433e948be7","tid":1520904,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"咩最後一戰呀？明明就係無限之戰，你對手係赤納粹，有二三十年要捱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日關鍵係人數，唔係勇武"},{"pid":"0dcd4a9259f081af0ebdc27f4a56051d2d071493","tid":1520904,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike